      "uco-core:name": "Victim B mails ~$140,000 cash via UPS at co-conspirators' direction (from 2022-02-10)",
      "uco-core:description": "Directed by callers posing as DOJ agents to transfer her money 'for safekeeping'; Victim B kept receipts and a journal of all transactions. In total she withdrew $300,000 between 2022-02-10 and 2022-03-11. Source: PACER Doc 61 (factual_basis), pp. 6-7",
