      "uco-core:description": "Victim A was sent to the Santa Fe Cattle Company parking lot at Hammond Square Mall with a sealed cash box; Keel (driven to the pickup by Panchal) gave the code word and took the box. Source: PACER Doc 28 (superseding_indictment), Count 1 para. D.9; Source: PACER Doc 61 (factual_basis), pp. 2, 4",
