      "uco-core:name": "Post-arrest $1,000,000 offer to Victim A to drop the charges (2022-04-04)",
      "uco-core:description": "After Keel's arrest, the same spoofed number called Victim A offering $1,000,000 by wire transfer if she would drop the charges and release 'their guy'. Source: PACER Doc 61 (factual_basis), p. 4",
