      "uco-core:name": "JPSO warrant search of Keel's La Quinta Inn room",
      "uco-core:description": "Recovered tickets showing Keel flew Tampa Bay to Seattle on 2022-03-31 and Seattle to New Orleans arriving 2022-04-03; the room was reserved for two guests on the card ending 5885. Source: PACER Doc 61 (factual_basis), pp. 4-5",
