      "uco-core:name": "HSI records attribution: airline, hotel, payment-card, and bank records",
      "uco-core:description": "Delta/United/Alaska records, La Quinta records, Citibank records for the card ending 5885, and Victim B's bank records ($300,000 withdrawn 2022-02-10 to 2022-03-11) tied Panchal to the bookings and quantified the losses. Source: PACER Doc 61 (factual_basis), pp. 4-5, 7",
